content:
Implementing and executing effective service processes is a key factor for customer satisfaction. Building service processes and configuring integrations with external systems is a time-consuming and complex task.

Service agents can launch these service processes and get started with critical customer service operations. Customer community users can directly launch these service processes from a self-service portal and quickly submit their service process requests.

The Notify Travel Plans service process simplifies the travel experience for your customers, enabling them to provide notice about their upcoming trips.
The Update Email or Phone service process allows your customers to maintain accurate contact information, receive timely information, and enhance security through proper communication.
The Stop Check Payment service process allows your customers to cancel a check payment, which isnâ€™t processed yet.
The Report and Replace Cards service process allows your customers to report stolen cards, block cards, and start a replacement card request.
The Order Checkbook service process allows your customers to order a checkbook.
The Request Statement Copies service process allows your customers to request statement copies for their financial accounts.
The Transfer Funds to Own Account service process allows your customers to transfer funds between their financial accounts.
The Manage Standing Instructions service process allows your customers to add or modify instructions for setting up recurring and timely payments.
The Manage Beneficiaries service process allows your customers to add, modify, or delete beneficiaries who receive the benefit of funds from their financial accounts.
The Request Loan Payoff Statement service process simplifies the way customers can manage and repay their loans.

Add your company logo to Salesforce Classic documents and incorporate the logo into an email template. Add the Source System ID field to page layouts and connect your Salesforce and MuleSoft instances for integration with core banking systems.

Agents can launch OmniScripts from a person account to capture service requests, guiding users in capturing customer service requests.
title: Implementing Retail Banking Service Processes for Financial Services Cloud
